---
title: Broiled Salmon and Garlicky Shrimp with Mash and Tomato-Pepper Sauce
description: This seafood feast features all the best of the ocean! Garlicky shrimp and Mediterranean-spiced salmon come together with chive mash for a jam-packed plate of deliciousness. An easy sauce made of sautéed tomatoes and sweet peppers adds gorgeous colour to the plate and makes the salmon pop!
